Text: Institute for Advance Study in Musical Theatre Cc I just wanted to drop you an email to touch base on the Institute Yesterday I went to see Stuarts workshop of three new original musical theatre productions at UH It was very exciting and even more so knowing that we can take his efforts to a new level with the establishment of the Insitute Anyway I just wanted to check in with you I hope all is well and look forward to hearing back from you L PS congrats on the Arena vote
